# StudIt project rules

Before editing code, read **AGENTS.md** at the repository root.

## Frontend (required)

- Structure: `pages/<feature>/index.tsx`, `routes/routes.tsx`, `api/command.ts`, `stores/`, `mocks/data/`
- Use `@/` imports. API calls only via `@/api/command`, not raw `fetch` or `axios` in pages.
- Auth: `useAuthStore` from `@/stores/authStore`. Protected routes: `PrivateRoute` from `@/routes/privateRoute`.
- MSW: handlers in `mocks/handlers.ts`, data in `mocks/data/`. Do not edit `public/mockServiceWorker.js`.
- Env: `VITE_SERVER_URL`, `VITE_USE_MOCK`.

## Backend

- Spring Boot under `backend/`, REST under `/api`, Java package `com.studit`.

## Do not

- Reintroduce Django `source_code/` or flat `pages/FooPage.tsx` at src root.
- Commit `frontend/.env` secrets.
